Mr. Oklopkov ' s replacement will not take place: the post of technical director is likely to be abolished and the functional director will be deployed to the offices of CENI.
The technical director of the Eastern and Deputy Director-General of CENI for Technology Development, Andrei Oklopkov, moved to work at the Khrunichev GPCC, JO was briefed by the top managers of several space industries and a government official.
"He's been working in a new position for weeks," I'm told by I.A.'s interlocutors in the industry.
It was not possible to obtain an operational comment from CENCI on Thursday, and Mr. Oklopkov himself was not available for comments.
